title: Brothers Osborne Perform In-Studio With Their Dad + Bobby Geeks Out On Craig Robinson From ‘The Office’ + Scary Movie Music Game
itunes:title: Brothers Osborne Perform In-Studio With Their Dad + Bobby Geeks Out On Craig Robinson From ‘The Office’ + Scary Movie Music Game
description:
Brothers Osborne perform in studio with their dad. The family band, "Deuce and a Quarter", plays an original song written by their dad. Bobby talks to Craig Robinson about a new podcast called “Make It Up As We Go” and his character on "The Office”. Plus, we play a fun game to see if the show members can guess the scary movie based only on the music!
